36
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:49,850
modulation, where essentially
it's the frequency of a

37
00:02:49,850 --> 00:02:54,850
sinusoid that's changing
depending on the signal that's

38
00:02:54,850 --> 00:02:59,460
