39
00:02:59,460 --> 00:03:03,200
Now sinusoidal amplitude,
frequency, and phase

40
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:07,950
modulation are extremely
important topics and ideas in

41
00:03:07,950 --> 00:03:11,570
