98
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:39,550
And then of course the resulting
output is the

99
00:06:39,550 --> 00:06:41,640
modulated output.

100
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:45,890
Now to analyze this, since we
have multiplication in the

101
00:06:45,890 --> 00:06:49,350
